<juve. evan. 1.685>	At si quos nimium fallax inlexque malorum
<juve. evan. 1.686>	Planities suasit deformi lubrica lapsu,
<juve. evan. 1.687>	Adripit hos pronosque trahit uelut impetus amnis,
<juve. evan. 1.688>	Aut alacer sonipes ruptis effrenus habenis,
<juve. evan. 1.689>	Aut rectoris egens uentosa per aequora puppis.
<juve. evan. 1.>	ADTENDITE A FALSIS PROPHETIS
<juve. evan. 1.690>	Obseruate illos, falso qui nomine uobis
<juve. evan. 1.691>	Insidias faciunt appellanturque profetae.
<juve. evan. 1.692>	Hos ouium species uestit, sed saeua luporum
<juve. evan. 1.693>	Pectora fraude tegunt, lacerantque incauta trahentes
